data.description: Investor Special in Brooklyn! Perfect project for the winter in a wonderful location. Large Corner lot with full, wood privacy fence connects to this Bungalow home. Two first floor bedrooms, Full bathroom, Living Room and Eat in Kitchen plus a spacious primary bedroom up need some TLC to bring them back to life. The full, finished basement has a bar area, room for extra living space, storage, laundry space with washer and dryer plus plumbed for a toilet. All appliances stay in the kitchen too. Newer electric panel and hot water tank.  Central air unit does not work but since already there, it makes it easier to update. Detached 2 car garage needs a makeover too. This will keep you busy through the winter with an opportunity for an amazing end result.  Convenient location close to shopping, schools and highway access.
